#: ../client/about.ts:9
msgid ""
"\"To me, how we've got here today is owing to Stockfish in a BIG way. They "
"rallied global volunteers to come together in the open-source spirit and "
"create such a powerful engine for FREE. That's a lot of great minds and "
"computing power they've managed to harness."
msgstr ""
"\"Para min, o feito de estar hoxe aquí debémosllo nunha GRANDE parte a "
"Stockfish. Lograron xuntar a voluntarios arredor do mundo, no espírito "
"colaborativo do código aberto, para crearen tan poderoso motor GRATUÍTO. Iso"
" foi unha chea de grandes mentes e poder de computación moi ben "
"aproveitados."

#: ../client/about.ts:10
msgid ""
"Then we've got Lichess to thank. Lichess was also born out of the same open-"
"source spirit, and it too drew in great people as well. Once Lichess "
"incorporated Stockfish as its brains, the rest is history."
msgstr ""
"Despois tamén temos que agradecer a Lichess. Lichess tamén naceu do mesmo "
"espírito do código aberto, e tamén xuntou a moita xente. Así que Lichess "
"incluiu Stockfish como cerebro, o resto é historia."

#: ../client/about.ts:11
msgid ""
"Lichess enables the online, real-time, and competitive aspects of game-play."
" They also bring the enormous power of Stockfish to the masses, who can now "
"benefit from it without configuring a local GUI. I believe this development "
"turns out to be of great consequence and significance."
msgstr ""
"Lichess ofrece xogar de forma competitiva, en tempo real e online. Tamén "
"trouxo o enorme poder de cálculo de Stockfish para todo o mundo, que agora "
"se pode beneficiar do seu uso sen ter que configurar unha GUI local. Creo "
"que este desenvolvemento resulta ser dunha grande importancia e "
"consecuencia."

#: ../client/about.ts:12
msgid ""
"Later on, developers close to the Lichess project eventually extended "
"Stockfish into Multivariant-Stockfish, in order to support Crazyhouse et al."
" The father of Fairy-Stockfish, Fabian, is also one of those devs (still) "
"working on that fork, and he later took several steps further in terms of "
"variant support and extensibility. Thus Fairy-Stockfish was born, so "
"powerful because it builds on the Stockfish project."
msgstr ""
"Máis tarde, desenvolvedores achegados ao proxecto Lichess deron en estender "
"Stockfish a Multivariant-Stockfish, para soportar Crazyhouse e compañía. O "
"pai de Fairy-Stockfish, Fabian, tamén é un deses desenvolvedores (todavía) "
"traballando nese fork, e máis tarde deu varios pasos máis en termos de "
"soporte de variantes e estensibilidade. Polo tanto Fairy-Stockfish naceu tan"
" poderoso porque se baseou no proxecto Stockfish."

#: ../client/about.ts:13
msgid ""
"Then comes our beloved pychess-variants, which again very smartly harnesses "
"the underlying superpowers of the big projects. Same online, real-time, and "
"competitive aspects. Same clean and familiar Lichess look and feel. Plus the"
" power of Stockfish!\""
msgstr ""
"Despois xordeu a nosa querida pychess-variants, quen de novo aproveita de "
"forma intelixente os incribles superpoderes dos grandes proxectos. Cos "
"mesmos aspectos de competición, en tempo real e online. Co mesmo aspecto "
"limpo e familiar de Lichess. E mais co poder de Stockfish!"

